_______________________________________________________________________________
"Teleport Object" 
        The psionicist can teleport an object from his location to the
        location of another player, like the UPS service in the post
        office.  For a slightly higher SP cost, the psionicist can
        teleport an object to the guild storage room.
 
SP Cost:  20 (40 to guild)    Guild Level:  10    Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  telobj <object> to <target>
